{"tid":872841,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"漢能宣布私有化？","createTime":"2018-10-23T04:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T15:01:47.000Z","uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"48a322be50a3c795a3a660888e01237a4f9bd4e9","tid":872841,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"漢能宣布私有化 要約收購價格為每股不低於5港元<br />\n<br />\n來源：2018-10-23 11:30 網易財經<br />\n<br />\n10月23日，漢能移動能源控股集團公告稱，鑑於漢能薄膜發電集團有限公司（HK 00566）（以下簡稱&ldquo;上市公司&rdquo;）停牌已經超過三年，出於對中小股東利益的保護，經漢能移動能源控股集團有限公司第二屆第7次董事會批准，我司決定對持有上市公司股票的所有投資人發出私有化要約，收購價格為每股不低於5港元，以現金收購或股票置換，私有化之後公司擬在國內A股上市。<br />\n<br />\n公告稱，我公司已於2018年10月12日向上市公司發出了私有化建議。上市公司於2018年10月18日召開董事會進行了專題研究，並做出決議：一致同意我司提出的私有化建議。上市公司要求我司根據香<br />\n港公司收購及合併守則要求完善落實該提議方案，上市公司將按照相關法律程序報相關機構審批。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc787dce4654533df20759be56a2574c085ee0c","tid":872841,"uid":11283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:15:52.000Z","msg":"班散戶有救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fec5182834b0ef47239e317c76b57f6ce3dc2a","tid":872841,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"wtf 5蚊"},{"pid":"f1837eafb05cb2dcdda7b6f09a6e03270f279bac","tid":872841,"uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"果陣場外交易好似得番2毫子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對散戶黎講，5蚊好好了<br />\n好多應該預咗total lost"},{"pid":"9178faef48dcd9c11568ea4a1375df5004035e52","tid":872841,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"網易財經條link<br />\n（殘體字，慎入）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://3g.163.com/money/article/DUQ3U30M00258169.html?clickfrom=channel2018_money_index_newslist#child=index&amp;offset=5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3g.163.com%2Fmoney%2Farticle%2FDUQ3U30M00258169.html%3Fclickfrom%3Dchannel2018_money_index_newslist%23child%3Dindex%26offset%3D5&d=MxlQAsTwfMfJU6fmmQTBWf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=aeb415fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://3g.163.com/money/article/DUQ3U30M00258169.html?clickfrom=channel2018_money_index_newslist#child=index&amp;offset=5</a>"},{"pid":"6136887036bbd62430a4a2264b4d0c0ac3477457","tid":872841,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"5蚊 賺撚左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3664fb1fbc815d6fbbf8bbb89a292a06622c4a57","tid":872841,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"擺到變左化石未<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b494665258a708694945d0026c225b1a6694d3","tid":872841,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3664fb1fbc815d6fbbf8bbb89a292a06622c4a57","tid":872841,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"擺到變左化石未<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"應該都變咗化石啦<br />\n3年，呢個世界已經天翻地覆"},{"pid":"1dc1fd82e34852748cb9998b9b41918b93f33019","tid":872841,"uid":62506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"點解咁有良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9680d2e8568c9d9c5bf4156d2347eebc33f3d0","tid":872841,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"我一定要賣比佢？？"},{"pid":"eb36ac010851c1fc523055f9b4fa603b38c5d0b9","tid":872841,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f9680d2e8568c9d9c5bf4156d2347eebc33f3d0","tid":872841,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-